            "Subsection": "e",
            "Content": "The Contractor shall submit one (1) end of year training completion report for each training site and one (1) end of year report for all of the providers combined sites, if applicable, to RSI within thirty (30) calendar days from the completion of training, but no later than December 15th of the Contract year."
          },
          {
            "Subsection": "f",
            "Content": "Because the data collected will include personal information, the Contractor shall take all required measures to ensure data security and shall indemnify RSI against any potential breach of information."
